---
title: Election Lifecycle Flow
---
flowchart LR
    subgraph P1["Setup"]
        direction TB
        S1([Start])
        S2[Deploy Contract]
        S3[Created Phase]
        S4[startRegistration]
        S5[Registration]
        S6[Student Reg]
        S7[Admin Verify]
        S8[Merkle Rebuild]
        S9[Candidate Reg]
        S10{Ok?}
        S11[startVoting]
    end
    
    subgraph P2["Voting"]
        direction TB
        T1[Voting Phase]
        T2[Connect Wallet]
        T3[Merkle Proof]
        T4[castVote Tx]
        T5[Verify + Sync]
        T6{Ok?}
        T7[endElection]
    end
    
    subgraph P3["End"]
        direction TB
        U1[Ended Phase]
        U2[Winner Select]
        U3[Finalize]
        U4[Archive]
        U5{Again?}
        U6[New Cycle]
        U7([Finish])
    end
    
    S11 --> T1
    T7 --> U1
    S10 -->|No| S6
    T6 -->|No| T2
    
